OL,3,CCould feeding gulls become a finable
OL,4,Coffence?
OL,6,FFeeding gulls could become a fineable
OL,7,Foffence in some areas of Scotland, as
OL,8,Fa council has put forward plans to
OL,9,Fintroduce a new by-law.
OL,11,FIt was proposed by East Berwickshire
OL,12,Fcouncillor James Anderson, following
OL,13,Fseveral attacks on people in Eyemouth
OL,14,Fand the surrounding areas.
OL,16,FA Scottish Borders Council meeting
OL,17,Fheard in August 2024 that seven
OL,18,Fchildren were left with cuts on their
OL,19,Fscalps in the space of one month due
OL,20,Fto attacks from herring gulls - a
OL,21,Fprotected species.
