OL,3,CCould feeding gulls become a finable
OL,4,Coffence?
OL,6,FIn 2019 this practice became a paid-
OL,7,Ffor service, and only three requests
OL,8,Fwere made. As such, it was deemed
OL,9,Feconomically unviable and was ended in
OL,10,Fthe same year.
OL,12,FCllr Anderson said: "Residents and
OL,13,Fbusinesses along the coast know how
OL,14,Fserious the gull problem has become.
OL,16,F"NatureScot have been clear that the
OL,17,Fmost effective action we can take is
OL,18,Fto remove food at source, but at
OL,19,Fpresent the council has no enforcement
OL,20,Fpowers to stop deliberate feeding.
