OL,6,F"A targeted by-law would give the
OL,7,Fcouncil the tools it needs to address
OL,8,Fa long-standing problem, protect the
OL,9,Fpublic, and help move gull populations
OL,10,Fback to their natural cliff habitats."
OL,12,FIf councillors approve the plans, a
OL,13,Fdraft by-law and enforcement proposals
OL,14,Fwill be drawn up, and it will go to a
OL,15,Ffull public consultation.
